<lyrics>[V1]
 1-(ạ̉nạ ạ̉sf ạ̉nạ gẖlṭạn wnạdm qlby yạ sydy
 ʿly̱ ạlmạḍy ʿly̱ ạlʿṣyạn wmsmạr dqyth bạ̹ydy)2
 ạlqrạr- (sạmḥny .sạmḥny sạmḥny mạ knsẖ qṣdy ạ̉bʿd ʿnk yạ sydy
 sạmḥny .sạmḥny mn ʿạlm kạn fy qlby wnsyt ḥbk yạ sydy)2
 sạmḥny wkẖly ḥbk ygẖfr kl ạldẖnwb
 sạmḥny wkẖly dmk ystr kl ạlʿywb
 2-(snyn ḍạʿt wạ̉nạ fy ʿnạd mạkntsẖ bsmʿ lṣwtk
 snyn rạḥt ạ̉klhạ jrạd mạ qdrtsẖ qymẗ mwtk)2
 3-(ạ̉nạ rạjʿ ạ̉nạ msẖtạq lḥḍnk ạldạfy yạ sydy
 wqlby wạlḥnyn ạ̉sẖwạq ldmk ạlsẖạfy yạsydy)2</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉nạ ậsf</title>
</song>